headline: Labcorp Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: Labcorp Holdings Inc. (NYSE: LH), a global leader of innovative and comprehensive laboratory services, announced today that its Board of Directors has declared a cash dividend of $0.72 per share of common stock. The dividend will be payable on June 11, 2025, to stockholders of record as of the close of business on May 29, 2025.
